      <title>沙特阿拉伯有望从阿美石油出售中获得 112 亿美元收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/aramco-sale-set-to-raise-at-least-11-2-billion-for-saudi-arabia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美的巨额股票发行将为利雅得筹集至少 112 亿美元，这是约三年来全球最大的此类交易，将有助于为数万亿美元的经济转型计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/aramco-sale-set-to-raise-at-least-11-2-billion-for-saudi-arabia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 00:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 重申有条件加息，油价缩减周跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 OPEC+ 部分成员国重申其恢复暂停供应的计划取决于市场状况后，石油期货缩减了本周的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 23:29:33 GMT</pubDate>
